  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Business Development Executive (RegTech / KYC Solution)",
  "description": "<h3>1. Lead Generation & Prospecting</h3><ul><li><p>Identify and build a pipeline of <strong>qualified leads</strong> within:</p><ul><li><p>Law firms  </p></li><li><p>Corporate service providers  </p></li><li><p>MAS-regulated financial institutions  </p></li></ul></li><li><p>Maintain accurate lead records in CRM and track engagement status</p></li></ul><h3>2. Outreach & Initial Engagement</h3><ul><li><p>Articulate KYC and AML <strong>pain points</strong> </p></li><li>Secure <strong>introductory calls, demos, or discovery meetings</strong> for senior team members</li></ul><ul><li>Support follow-ups and early-stage deal progression</li></ul><p> Required Experience & Skills</p><h3>Core Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>1–4 years of experience in:</p><ul><li><p>Lead generation, business development, or sales support <strong>OR</strong></p></li><li><p>Compliance, corporate services, or financial services with commercial exposure</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Strong understanding of (or ability to quickly learn):</p><ul><li><p>KYC / AML concepts</p></li><li><p>Regulated professional services environment in Singapore</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Professional written and verbal communication skills</p></li><li><p>Comfortable engaging <strong>compliance officers, lawyers, and decision makers</strong></p></li></ul><h3>Preferred / Advantageous</h3><p><p>Prior experience selling or supporting:</p><ul><li><p>RegTech, legal tech, compliance software, or SaaS</p></li></ul><p>Existing network within law firms, CSPs, or financial institutions<br /></p><h2>What We Offer</h2><ul><li><p>Performance-based incentives</p></li><li><p>Training on regulatory frameworks and KYC best practices</p></li></ul></p>",
